<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-400/10 via-storehouse-50 to-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">
        Why we chose this name.
      </h2>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold-500 pl-6 py-4 bg-white rounded-r-lg shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-lg font-display text-slate-700 italic">
          "Bring the whole tithe into the storehouse, that there may be food in my house."
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500 not-italic">
          - Malachi 3:10
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          In ancient Israel, the storehouse was where the community stored provision - grain, oil, wine. It was a place of abundance, set aside for both regular needs and times of crisis.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's what we're helping you build:
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-storehouse-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-storehouse-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 0c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-700 pt-2">A place to store provision for lean times</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-giving/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-giving" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-700 pt-2">A practice of putting generosity first</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-saving/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-saving" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-700 pt-2">A foundation of trust rather than anxiety</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
